reviews.reviewText: Beautiful journal, full size for plenty of writing space, 368 pgs enough for daily entries. Soft leather cover, ribbon place marker, snap closure and pen included. Can't wait to start the new year using it as a prayer journal.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Just simply beautiful & just as described. The leather embroidery is so pretty & subtle. The cover is soft. Has a ribbon so you don’t lose your place. Snap closure is solid & strong. The pages are nice to write on. I personally don’t like the pen, I like a thinner & fine point pen.It’s an all around perfect journal. 100% happy.
